org.eclipse.papyrus.MARTE.MARTE_DesignModel.SRM.SW_Concurrency

Interface MemoryPartition

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, Resource, SwResource
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    MemoryPartitionImpl

    public interface MemoryPartition
extends SwResource
    A representation of the model object 'Memory Partition'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Concurrent Resources
    • Memory Spaces
    • Fork
    • Exit
    • Base Namespace

    See Also:
    SW_ConcurrencyPackage.getMemoryPartition()
